    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Gradation 1 against a required Gradation 2; this shortfall is acknowledged and compensated by N=11 specimen replication across two independent laboratories and all three QoI comparisons meeting pre-specified acceptance bounds with E/uval well below 1.96. The overall credibility package is judged sufficient to support the 510(k) submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw at Medium model risk level.",
